column2: SELECT    m.designation, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,    n.objid, n.distance,    o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2,    s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning,    p.z as zPhot, p.zErr as zPhotErr,    o.dered_u, o.dered_g, o.dered_i, o.dered_r, o.dered_z into mydb.rgz_xid_out_# from mydb.wise1# AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n      JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid      LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS s on o.specObjID=s.specObjID      LEFT JOIN Photoz as p on p.objID=o.objid      WHERE o.mode = # AND o.type = #
